{
  "stem": "5758.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Then he really showed-- wanted to show his authority and started whipping us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] came lunchtime, we-- they brought a big bucket of soup, hot water out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But it was very thin soup, nothing in it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And we ate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "We stopped work for half an hour.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "We sat maybe in a building and ate the soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And then we continued working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when it-- just before it gets dark at night, we lined up five in a row.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "The capo counted us, and we marched back through the gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Music again, march, a German march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "Again, mutzen up!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Greeting the SS.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And went to the barracks, and we got our-- another liter of soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "This eating of the soup, we always try to be towards with the end of the queue, because in the big bucket, on the bottom, maybe vegetables were sitting.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "But we were whipped into queue, to line up, because nobody wanted to be the very first one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And we found, really, that our blockalteste, who was giving out the soup, really did it very good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "He-- he mixed it around, and-- and somehow or other, we did get, in the evening, a much better soup than we did at lunch.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I forgot to mention that in the morning, we had a coffee, or break-- ersatz, they called it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Like liquid-- hot liquid and a piece of bread and a piece of margarine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "Sometimes we had-- once a week or twice a week, we had maybe a piece of sausage to go with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "So this was our diet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was extremely lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "I told you that  I befriended a Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "Robert Weiss.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
